OL,3,CPlastic surgeon sentenced for trying
OL,4,Cto murder fellow doctor in work feud
OL,6,FA plastic surgeon has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto life in prison, with a minimum term
OL,8,Fof 22 years, for trying to kill a
OL,9,Ffellow surgeon by stabbing him, after
OL,10,Fhe attempted to set his house on fire.
OL,12,FPeter Brooks will only serve a minimum
OL,13,Fof 17 years and 223 days, as he has
OL,14,Falready spent some time in custody.
