OL,3,CPlastic surgeon sentenced for trying
OL,4,Cto murder fellow doctor in work feud
OL,6,FDr Jonathan (Peter) Brooks, 61, was
OL,7,Fconvicted of two counts of attempted
OL,8,Fmurder, attempted arson with intent to
OL,9,Fendanger life, and possession of a
OL,10,Fknife in a public place after he
OL,11,Fattacked former colleague Graeme Perks
OL,12,Fin the early hours of January 14, 2021.
OL,14,FJailing him at a court sitting in
OL,15,FLoughborough, Judge Mr Justice
OL,16,FPepperall said Brooks had committed
OL,17,F"appalling" crimes after setting off
OL,18,Ffrom his home on a "murderous
OL,19,Fexpedition".
