OL,4,Cto murder fellow doctor in work feud
OL,6,FJurors deliberated for more than 12
OL,7,Fhours before finding Brooks guilty of
OL,8,Fall the charges against him.
OL,10,FProsecutors said Brooks, doused the
OL,11,Fground floor of the property in petrol
OL,12,Fbefore stabbing Mr Perks, who he
OL,13,F"hated" because he was giving evidence
OL,14,Fin a work disciplinary hearing against
OL,15,Fthe defendant.
OL,17,FBoth men are former plastic surgeons
OL,18,Fat Nottingham City Hospital.
