OL,4,Cto murder fellow doctor in work feud
OL,6,FBrooks, who was "voluntarily absent"
OL,7,Ffrom his month-long trial because he
OL,8,Fwas on hunger strike and said he would
OL,9,F"rather be dead than incarcerated",
OL,10,Fdid not appear in person for the
OL,11,Fsentencing hearing on Monday (9 June)
OL,12,Fafter refusing to leave his cell.
OL,14,FStephen Leslie KC, defending, said
OL,15,FBrooks had said he was too unwell to
OL,16,Fmake the journey to court and instead
OL,17,Flistened to proceedings via video link
OL,18,Ffrom HMP Norwich.
