OL,6,FMr Justice Pepperall previously told
OL,7,Fthe court that on "no fewer than eight
OL,8,Foccasions" since 2021, Brooks,
OL,9,Fformerly of Landseer Road, Southwell,
OL,10,Fhad "used hunger strikes or the threat
OL,11,Fof some other self-harm to achieve
OL,12,Fsome advantage".
OL,14,FBrooks' convictions followed a four-
OL,15,Fyear series of legal hearings,
OL,16,Fincluding a mistrial and seven other
OL,17,Faborted trial dates.
