OL,6,FMr Perks, who was 65 at the time, had
OL,7,Fretired the month before the attack
OL,8,Fbut suffered "extremely life-
OL,9,Fthreatening" injuries to his liver,
OL,10,Fintestines and pancreas, and was given
OL,11,Fa 95% chance of death.
OL,13,FLoughborough Court heard Dr Brooks, a
OL,14,Fspecialist in burns and plastics,
OL,15,Fcycled to Mr Perks' house in Halam,
OL,16,FNottinghamshire, in the early hours of
OL,17,FJanuary 14, 2021.
OL,19,FProsecutors said Brooks doused the
OL,20,Fground floor of the property in petrol
OL,21,Fbefore stabbing Mr Perks.
