OL,11,Fby the head torch of a man he thought
OL,12,Fwas wearing a balaclava before being
OL,13,Fstabbed in the abdomen, leaving him in
OL,14,Fintensive care.
OL,16,FHe said he could not see the
OL,17,Fintruder's face because they had a
OL,18,Fheadlight on and he thought they might
