OL,7,Fintensive care for eight days, and in
OL,8,Fhospital the following three weeks.
OL,10,FGiving analysis on the trial around
OL,11,Fthe time of conviction, ITV News
OL,12,FCentral journalist Peter Bearne said
OL,13,Fhe had 'never covered a trial quite
OL,14,Flike this'.
